difficulty: Poor formatting made some of the questions very difficult to answer. When I could barely read a table, I all but knew I was getting the answer wrong.
format: When I could clearly access large chunks of information, I was satisfied; as this let me better compare info. Conversely, when a table required too much scrolling, that is when I became frustrated.
comments: Overall, I enjoyed participating in this study. I was honestly surprised at the number of well formatted tables.
